---
title: 路由token鉴权,界面跳转有延迟
description: 路由token鉴权,界面跳转有延迟,请问怎么解决?
---

# 使用路由token鉴权,界面跳转有延迟？下面是我的代码

```javascript
export default ({ app }) => {
  app.router.beforeEach((to, from, next) => {
    if (to.path === '/login') return next();

    if (process.client) {
      let t = window.sessionStorage.getItem('token');
      if (!t) {
        next('/login');
        return;
      }
    }

    next();
  });
}

```
